- cs.SD (Software Development) is less likely as the paper does not focus on software development, but rather on theoretical properties of betweenness centrality profiles.
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is less likely as the paper does not involve numerical methods or algorithms, but rather focuses on theoretical properties.
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is less likely as the paper does not involve game theory, but rather focuses on graph theory.
